  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This ice-blue half-mask is adorned with a wicked silver grin that covers the wearer's mouth, leaving the rest of the face uncovered. You gain a +2 item bonus to Intimidation checks.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2 </span>envision, Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The mask emits a soul-chilling scream that deals @Damage[6d10[void]] damage to each living creature in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:20] (@Check[type:fortitude|dc:25|basic:true] save).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply a casting of <em>wail of the banshee</em>.</p>"
